                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-444-18360201 t18360201-444-punishment-39"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fifth Jury, before Mr. Sergeant Arabin</hi>.</p>
